    "m_SourceType": 1,
    "m_FunctionName": "WhiteBalance",
    "m_FunctionSource": "",
    "m_FunctionSourceUsePragmas": true,
    "m_FunctionBody": "// Girişler: In (Vector3 linear), Temperature (Float -100..100), Tint (Float -100..100)\r\n// Çıkış: Out (Vector3)\r\n\r\nfloat t1 = Temperature / 65.0;\r\nfloat t2 = Tint / 65.0;\r\n\r\n// referans beyaz noktanın CIE xy değeri (D65)\r\nfloat wbX = 0.31271 - t1 * (t1 < 0.0 ? 0.1 : 0.05);\r\nfloat standardY = 2.87 * wbX - 3.0 * wbX * wbX - 0.27509507;\r\nfloat wbY = standardY + t2 * 0.05;\r\n\r\n// CIE xy -> CAT02 LMS\r\nfloat bigY = 1.0;\r\nfloat bigX = bigY * wbX / wbY;\r\nfloat bigZ = bigY * (1.0 - wbX - wbY) / wbY;\r\nfloat lCoef =  0.7328 * bigX + 0.4296 * bigY - 0.1624 * bigZ;\r\nfloat mCoef = -0.7036 * bigX + 1.6975 * bigY + 0.0061 * bigZ;\r\nfloat sCoef =  0.0030 * bigX + 0.0136 * bigY + 0.9834 * bigZ;\r\n\r\nfloat3 w1 = float3(0.949237, 1.03542, 1.08728); // D65\r\nfloat3 balance = float3(w1.x / lCoef, w1.y / mCoef, w1.z / sCoef);\r\n\r\n// linear <-> LMS matrisleri (Unity Core)\r\nfloat3x3 LIN_TO_LMS = float3x3(\r\n    3.90405e-1, 5.49941e-1, 8.92632e-3,\r\n    7.08416e-2, 9.63172e-1, 1.35775e-3,\r\n    2.31082e-2, 1.28021e-1, 9.36245e-1\r\n);\r\nfloat3x3 LMS_TO_LIN = float3x3(\r\n     2.85847e+0, -1.62879e+0, -2.48910e-2,\r\n    -2.10182e-1,  1.15820e+0,  3.24281e-4,\r\n    -4.18120e-2, -1.18169e-1,  1.06867e+0\r\n);\r\n\r\nfloat3 lms = mul(LIN_TO_LMS, In);\r\nlms *= balance;\r\nOut = mul(LMS_TO_LIN, lms);"
}

